data.description: **Multiple Offers Received. Highest and Best Due By Tuesday 1pm. Welcome Home! This home is what you have been waiting for, from the charming welcoming porch to the Beautiful inviting 2-Story Foyer.  This fantastic 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath with a beautiful Open Loft overlooking the living room space. Beautiful Kitchen with Granite Countertops and SS appliances, an island and so much space for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen area open to the Family Room creating an inviting atmosphere.  Wonderful 1st floor bedroom that can also be used as an office or any type of room your family may need. Open to so many possibilities. Updates have been done throughout this home.   Spacious Master bedroom with Vaulted Ceilings, large bath with dual sinks, a separate tub and shower. A un-finished basement ready for you to create that wonderful additional space. A Beautiful Updated patio for all your entertaining , fully fenced for your pets safety and includes a play set area for your little one's to play. This home has so much to offer. Great location, Desirable Columbia Station and Oswego School district.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours.
